msgid "Info Center"
msgstr "Informační centrum"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kinfocenter.appdata.xml:11
msgid "Learn about the system's hardware and status"
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kinfocenter.appdata.xml:13
msgid ""
"The Info Center provides you with a centralized and convenient overview of "
"your system and desktop environment."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kinfocenter.appdata.xml:15
msgid ""
"The information center is made up of multiple modules. Each module is a "
"separate application, but the information center organizes all of these "
"programs into a convenient location."
msgstr ""
"Informační centrum se skládá z celé řady modulů. Každý modul je ve "
"skutečnosti samostatná aplikace, informační centrum ale všechny tyto "
"aplikace sdružuje do jednoho místa."
